<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="Task Management Web Application built with vanilla JavaScript." />
  <title>Task Manager • Vanilla JS</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Skip link for keyboard users -->
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to main content</a>

  <header class="site-header" role="banner">
    <div class="container header-grid">
      <div class="brand">
        <span class="logo" aria-hidden="true">
          <!-- Inline SVG icon (no external libs) -->
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 12l3 3 7-7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <path d="M20 12a8 8 0 1 1-16 0 8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h1 class="title">Task Manager</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Create, organize, and complete tasks — fast.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <nav class="header-actions" aria-label="Primary actions">
        <button id="themeToggle" class="btn ghost" type="button" aria-label="Toggle theme" aria-pressed="false">
          <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌓</span>
          <span class="btn-text">Theme</span>
        </button>

        <button id="exportBtn" class="btn ghost" type="button" aria-label="Export tasks to JSON">
          <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">⬇️</span>
          <span class="btn-text">Export</span>
        </button>

        <!-- Styled label acts as button -->
        <label class="btn ghost file-btn" for="importFile" aria-label="Import tasks from JSON">
          <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">⬆️</span>
          <span class="btn-text">Import</span>
        </label>
        <input id="importFile" type="file" accept="application/json" class="sr-only" />

        <button id="seedBtn" class="btn ghost" type="button" aria-label="Add example tasks">
          <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">✨</span>
          <span class="btn-text">Demo</span>
        </button>

        <button id="clearBtn" class="btn danger ghost" type="button" aria-label="Clear all tasks">
          <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧹</span>
          <span class="btn-text">Clear</span>
        </button>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Toast notifications (ARIA live regions) -->
  <section class="toast-region" aria-label="Notifications">
    <div id="toastArea" class="toast-area" aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true"></div>
    <div id="alertArea" class="sr-only" aria-live="assertive" aria-atomic="true"></div>
  </section>

  <main id="main" class="site-main" role="main">
    <div class="container layout">
      <!-- Left: Add Task Form -->
      <section class="card" aria-labelledby="addTaskHeading">
        <header class="card-header">
          <h2 id="addTaskHeading">Add Task</h2>
          <p class="hint">Fields marked with <span aria-hidden="true">*</span><span class="sr-only">required</span> are required.</p>
        </header>

        <form id="taskForm" class="form" novalidate>
          <!-- Error summary -->
          <div id="errorSummary" class="error-summary" role="alert" aria-live="polite" hidden></div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="title">Title <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
            <input id="title" name="title" type="text" autocomplete="off"
                   placeholder="e.g., Finish Assignment 4"
                   aria-describedby="titleHelp titleError"
                   required minlength="2" maxlength="60" />
            <div id="titleHelp" class="help">2–60 characters.</div>
            <div id="titleError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="description">Description <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" rows="4"
                      placeholder="What needs to be done?"
                      aria-describedby="descHelp descError"
                      required minlength="5" maxlength="240"></textarea>
            <div id="descHelp" class="help">5–240 characters.</div>
            <div id="descError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="field">
              <label for="category">Category <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
              <select id="category" name="category" aria-describedby="catError" required>
                <option value="">Select…</option>
                <option>Personal</option>
                <option>Work</option>
                <option>Urgent</option>
                <option>School</option>
              </select>
              <div id="catError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
              <div class="help">Tip: You can type a custom category below.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
              <label for="customCategory">Custom category (optional)</label>
              <input id="customCategory" name="customCategory" type="text"
                     placeholder="e.g., Finance" maxlength="24" />
              <div class="help">Overrides the dropdown if provided.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <fieldset class="field">
            <legend>Priority <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></legend>
            <div class="radio-row" role="radiogroup" aria-describedby="priorityError">
              <label class="chip">
                <input type="radio" name="priority" value="low" required />
                <span>Low</span>
              </label>
              <label class="chip">
                <input type="radio" name="priority" value="medium" />
                <span>Medium</span>
              </label>
              <label class="chip">
                <input type="radio" name="priority" value="high" />
                <span>High</span>
              </label>
            </div>
            <div id="priorityError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
          </fieldset>

          <div class="actions">
            <button class="btn primary" type="submit">
              <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">➕</span>
              Add Task
            </button>
            <button class="btn" type="reset">
              <span class="btn-icon" aria-hidden="true">↩️</span>
              Reset
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </section>

      <!-- Right: Controls + List -->
      <section class="card" aria-labelledby="tasksHeading">
        <header class="card-header">
          <h2 id="tasksHeading">Tasks</h2>
          <p class="hint">Filter, search, and sort — updates happen instantly.</p>
        </header>

        <section class="toolbar" aria-label="Task controls">
          <div class="search-wrap">
            <label class="sr-only" for="search">Search tasks</label>
            <input id="search" type="search" placeholder="Search title, description, or category…"
                   aria-label="Search tasks by title, description, or category" />
            <span class="search-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔎</span>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-grid">
            <div class="field compact">
              <label for="filterCategory">Category</label>
              <select id="filterCategory" aria-label="Filter tasks by category">
                <option value="all">All</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="field compact">
              <label for="filterStatus">Status</label>
              <select id="filterStatus" aria-label="Filter tasks by status">
                <option value="all">All</option>
                <option value="active">Active</option>
                <option value="completed">Completed</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div class="field compact">
              <label for="sortBy">Sort</label>
              <select id="sortBy" aria-label="Sort tasks">
                <option value="createdDesc">Newest</option>
                <option value="createdAsc">Oldest</option>
                <option value="priorityDesc">Priority: High → Low</option>
                <option value="priorityAsc">Priority: Low → High</option>
                <option value="titleAsc">Title: A → Z</option>
                <option value="titleDesc">Title: Z → A</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="stats" aria-label="Task statistics">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-num" id="statTotal">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Total</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-num" id="statActive">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Active</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-num" id="statDone">0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Completed</span>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div id="emptyState" class="empty-state" hidden>
          <p><strong>No tasks found.</strong></p>
          <p class="hint">Try changing filters or add a new task.</p>
        </div>

        <ul id="taskList" class="task-list" aria-label="Task list"></ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer" role="contentinfo">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <p>Built with semantic HTML, accessible UI patterns, and vanilla JavaScript OOP.</p>
      <p class="hint">Tip: Press <kbd>/</kbd> to focus search.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Accessible Edit Modal -->
  <dialog id="editDialog" class="dialog" aria-labelledby="editTitle">
    <form method="dialog" id="editForm" class="dialog-body" novalidate>
      <header class="dialog-header">
        <h3 id="editTitle">Edit Task</h3>
        <button class="btn ghost icon" value="cancel" aria-label="Close edit dialog" type="submit">✖</button>
      </header>

      <input type="hidden" id="editId" />

      <div class="field">
        <label for="editTaskTitle">Title <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <input id="editTaskTitle" type="text" required minlength="2" maxlength="60" />
        <div id="editTitleError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <label for="editTaskDescription">Description <span class="req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
        <textarea id="editTaskDescription" rows="4" required minlength="5" maxlength="240"></textarea>
        <div id="editDescError" class="field-error" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="editCategory">Category</label>
          <input id="editCategory" type="text" maxlength="24" />
        </div>
        <div class="field">
          <label for="editPriority">Priority</label>
          <select id="editPriority" required>
            <option value="low">Low</option>
            <option value="medium">Medium</option>
            <option value="high">High</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dialog-actions">
        <button class="btn primary" id="saveEditBtn" type="submit" value="confirm">💾 Save</button>
        <button class="btn" type="submit" value="cancel">Cancel</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </dialog>

  <script src="app.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
# Task Manager (Vanilla JavaScript)

A multi-feature **Task Management Web Application** built with **semantic HTML**, **responsive CSS**, and **vanilla JavaScript** (no frameworks, no external libraries).  
This project demonstrates **DOM manipulation**, **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)**, and **event handling** through a clean, accessible user interface.

## Live Demo
- **Live App:** https://YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME.github.io/YOUR-REPO-NAME/

---

## Features (Assignment Requirements ✅)

### Task CRUD Operations
- **Create** tasks with: **title**, **description**, **priority** (low/medium/high), and **category**
- **Read/List** tasks dynamically (no page refresh)
- **Update/Edit** tasks using an accessible modal (`<dialog>`)
- **Delete** tasks instantly from the list

### Categories + Filtering
- Organize tasks into categories (e.g., Personal, Work, Urgent, School)
- Filter tasks by:
  - **Category**
  - **Status** (Active / Completed)

### Priority Notifications (3–5 seconds)
- On-screen notifications automatically disappear after 3–5 seconds
- **High-priority** tasks trigger special alerts when:
  - Added
  - Updated
  - Marked completed

### OOP Design
- `Task` class encapsulates task data and behaviors (update, toggle completion)
- `TaskManager` class manages state and operations:
  - add, update, delete, filter, sort, search
- Data persists using `localStorage`

### UI / UX
- Responsive layout for **desktop and mobile**
- **Search** tasks by title, description, or category
- Mark tasks **completed** (visual strike-through + state update)
- **Dark/Light Theme Toggle** saved to `localStorage`
- Instant UI updates via DOM rendering

---

## Extra Features (For “Excellent” ⭐)
- **Undo Delete** via toast action button (prevents accidental deletion)
- **Export Tasks** to JSON (download)
- **Import Tasks** from JSON (upload)
- Respects **prefers-reduced-motion** for accessibility
- Keyboard shortcut: press **/** to focus search

---

## Accessibility Highlights
- Semantic landmarks: `<header>`, `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<footer>`
- **Skip link** for keyboard navigation
- Proper labels and helper/error text with `aria-describedby`
- `aria-live` regions for notifications (screen-reader friendly)
- Strong `:focus-visible` styles
- Accessible edit modal using native `<dialog>`

